itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway welcome back former navy seal Ray “Cash” Care to discuss some of the crazy guests Drinkin’ Bros has had on the show, Ray tells us why staying moving all the time sheds off the pounds life nothing else, Joe Rogan moves his show solely to Spotify during the show, and Ray talks about his next step in the entertainment industry as co-founder and lead instructor of LTD(Leadership Team Development Training).
